title: The Art Book by Phaidon.pdf
description:
The Art Book by Editors of Phaidon Press 
1994 | ISBN: 0714836257, 0714829846 | English | 518 Pages | PDF | 66 MB

Winner of the Illustrated Book of the Year award in 1994, The Art Book has become a publishing phenomenon and a well-known event in the art book world. Reduced in size, making it light and highly portable, this new mini edition presents the same easy-to-use alphabetical guide to 500 of the world's greatest painters and sculptors. 500 color illustrations.

PS. Book was poorly scanned, blue cast allover, I just got it through Photoshop automatically (Auto color) and it got better. It needs more fine tuning, page by page and some paintings more lighten up, but I dont have a time for that. Book is very usefull and informative - Artist per page ..
